1.1) change <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  sun vortex</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->. upgrade it to 1450 damage for 392 mana (3.69 ratio)<br>
1.2) change <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  maelstrom of thunder</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->. lower mana cost to 480 (5 ratio before resists)<br>
1.3) change <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  black steel</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->. upgrade it to 1350 damage for 370 mana (3.64 ratio)<br>
1.4) change <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  firebolt of tallon</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->. upgrade it to 1500 damage for 395 mana (3.79 ratio)<br>
1.5) get rid of the summoned charm/mez spells<br>
1.6) this is off topic but i would really like to see all 60+ wizard draught spells have their mana cost reduced to 180, <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  or</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> their damage upgraded to 900.<br>
--<br>
<br>
2) <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  new spells/abilities i would like added</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->:<br>
2.1) <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  resistant companion</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->. this is available to all primary pet classes at 55 (mag nec and bst), and all secondary pet classes at 60 (ench, sk, shm).<br>
spell costs 200 mana, lasts for 5 minutes and causes the owners pet to take 40% less damage from aes than it would have otherwise. this does not effect direct damage spells.<br>
<br>
2.2)if possible, as a standard change, all pets will become unaffected by spells which involve manipulating its position on the z-axis (such as gflux) due to the high potential for this to cause them to poof. they will take damage as they would if it were any other ae, they just physically wont move.<br>
<br>
2.3) <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  scintillation upgrade</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> at level 61. 750 damage for 500 mana with a 4 second cast time and 8 second recast sounds good.<br>
<br>
2.4) signifigantly upgrade our current vs summoned nukes. add a new vs summoned nuke in place of the current mez/charm spells which does 1800 damage for 450 mana.<br>
<br>
2.5) add a new series of proc'ing weapons, and upgrade old weapons. <br>
L34: Staff of Symbols: add combat proc shock of blades (35 dmg spell)<br>
L39: Dagger of Symbols: add combat proc flame bolt (47 dmg spell)<br>
L49: new spell: Whip of Symbols: stats in line with the rest of the symbol/runes line and combat effect stun<br>
<br>
L51: new spell: runed sword of matter: combat proc Expulse Summoned (94 dmg)<br>
L53: new spell: runed crimson staff; procs shock of flame (96 dmg)<br>
L55: new spell: runed dagger of energy; better ratio, procs shock of spikes (176 dmg)<br>
L59: new spell: rune encrusted whip: titans clash (5 sec stun 50 dmg spell)<br>
<br>
2.6)  new burnout... all other pet classes get a new buff, but not mages. somethings wrong with that ;(<br>
