<br>
I'd like to see MS4 sure, but I'm guessing thats something that will be scooted in, in another expansion.<br>
<br>
TPP for sure, in fact replace any one damage spell for an upgrade to that one.<br>
<br>
Summoned only mez and charm leave in please.  I just hope since it's the planes we are talking here, they'll be plenty more places that have summoned critters.<br>
<br>
