<br>
AA abilities that increase AC on air pets, or HP on earth pets.  More useful stat items that not only focus a kind of pet but also give them automatic burnout III when summoned for instance.<br>
<br>
More options when it comes to abilities, perhaps a staff that summones earth pets that hit twice as slow but for twice as much damage.   Even if the overall doesn't give us more power but more choice I think a lot of mages would be happy right there.<br>
